#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kanagram; is a game based on anagrams of words: the puzzle is solved when "
"the letters of the scrambled word are put back in the correct order. There "
"is no limit on either time taken, or the number of attempts to solve the "
"word. Included with &kanagram; are several vocabularies ready to play, with "
"many more available from the Internet."
msgstr ""
"&kanagram; je igra, ki temelji na anagramih besed: uganka je rešena, ko se "
"črke premešane besede postavijo nazaj v pravilen vrstni red. Ni omejitev "
"niti glede časa niti števila poskusov razrešitve besede. V &kanagram; je "
"vključeno več besednjakov, ki so pripravljeni za predvajanje, še več jih je "
"na voljo na internetu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kanagram;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kanagram;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &kanagram;, showing the "
"main interface to the application. Much of the window is taken up by the "
"<interface>blackboard</interface>, where the puzzles are written, with the "
"<interface>filing cabinet</interface> on the right containing application "
"controls."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je zaslon, ki se prikaže ob zagonu &kanagram; in prikazuje glavni "
"vmesnik za aplikacijo. Velik del okna zavzema <interface>tabla</interface>, "
"kjer so zapisane uganke, z <interface>kartoteko</interface> na desni, ki "
"vsebuje kontrolnike aplikacij."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &kanagram;"
msgstr "Tukaj je zaslon, ki se prikaže ob zagonu &kanagram;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:77 index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kanagram; screenshot"
msgstr "&kanagram; posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Vocabulary Switcher</interface> (&PgUp; / &PgDn;) allows the "
"user to quickly <action>change the active vocabulary</action> by clicking "
"with the &LMB; on the arrows to <action>advance to the next vocabulary</"
"action> or to <action>return to the previously-played vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Preklopnik besedišča</interface> (&PgUp; / &PgDn;) omogoča "
"uporabniku, da hitro <action>spremeni aktivni besednjak</action> s klikom z "
"&LMB; na puščicah za <action>naprej na naslednji besednjak</action> ali za "
"<action>vrnitev na predhodno predvajan besednjak</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the center of the <interface>blackboard</interface> is the anagram puzzle "
"to be solved."
msgstr ""
"Na sredini <interface>table</interface> je anagramska uganka, ki jo je treba "
"rešiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the <guiicon>Start Timer</guiicon> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) button, and allows you to <action>start or "
"stop the scoring timer</action>."
msgstr ""
"To je gumb <guiicon>Zaženi časovnik</guiicon> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) in vam omogoča, da <action>zaženete "
"ali ustavite točkovanje časovnika</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>) button is clicked, a short sentence will "
"appear, <action>describing the current word puzzle</action>."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Namig</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>), se prikaže kratek stavek, ki "
"<action>opisuje trenutno besedno uganko</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Reveal Word</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>) button <action>solves the current word "
"puzzle</action>."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Razkrij besedo</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>) <action>reši trenutno besedno uganko</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Entry Box</interface> allows you to <action>input your "
"attempts</action> to solve the current word puzzle."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Vnosno polje</interface> vam omogoča, da <action>vnesete svoje "
"poskuse</action> za rešitev trenutne besedne uganke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Next Anagram</interface> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) button lets you switch to the next guess."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <interface>Naslednji anagram</interface> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) omogoča preklop na naslednje "
"ugibanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the <guiicon>Configure</guiicon> button, which <action>opens the "
"<guilabel>Configure</guilabel> &kanagram; dialog</action>."
msgstr ""
"To je gumb <guiicon>Konfiguriraj</guiicon>, ki <action>odpre "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel> &kanagram; pogovorno okno</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guiicon>Help</guiicon> button is special, in that it <action>reveals 3 "
"sub-buttons</action>. These buttons are shown when the <guiicon>Help</"
"guiicon> button is hovered over, and provide access to the "
"<guilabel>&kanagram; Handbook</guilabel> (this document), and the "
"<guilabel>About &kanagram;</guilabel> and <guilabel>About &kde;</guilabel> "
"dialogs:"
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guiicon>Pomoč</guiicon> je poseben, ker <action>razkrije 3 podgumbe</"
"action>. Ti gumbi so prikazani, ko miškin kazalec premaknete nad gumb "
"<guiicon>Pomoč</guiicon> in omogočajo dostop do <guilabel>&kanagram; "
"Priročnik</guilabel> (ta dokument) in pogovorni okni <guilabel>O &kanagram;</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>O &kde;</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "The 3 different states of the <guiicon>Help</guiicon> button"
msgstr "3 različna stanja gumba <guiicon>Pomoč</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guiicon>Change mode</guiicon> button to switch between 1 and 2 "
"player mode."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guiicon>Spremeni način</guiicon> za preklop med načinoma za "
"1 in 2 igralca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> button <action>closes the application</action>."
msgstr "Gumb <guiicon>Zapri</guiicon> <action>zapre aplikacijo</action>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing a game"
msgstr "Igranje igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that you are familiar with the user interface of &kanagram;, lets play a "
"game!"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko ste seznanjeni z uporabniškim vmesnikom &kanagram;, se igrajmo igro!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <interface>Vocabulary Switcher</interface>, <action>select the "
"vocabulary theme</action> that you would like to attempt. A word from this "
"vocabulary will then be presented in the middle of the "
"<interface>blackboard</interface>. Now, try and guess what word the jumble "
"of letters represents."
msgstr ""
"Z <interface>preklopnikom besedišča</interface> <action>izberite temo "
"besedišča</action>, ki jo želite preizkusiti. Beseda iz tega besedišča bo "
"nato predstavljena na sredini <interface>table</interface>. Zdaj pa "
"poskusite uganiti, katero besedo predstavlja zmešnjava črk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cannot guess what the word is, press the <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> "
"button to get some friendly advice from your friend in the <interface>filing "
"cabinet</interface>:"
msgstr ""
"Če ne morete uganiti, kaj je beseda, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Namig</"
"guibutton>, da dobite prijateljski nasvet od prijatelja v "
"<interface>kartoteki</interface>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kanagram; hint</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kanagram; namig</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; hint</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram; namig</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you think you know the correct answer, type the letters into the "
"<interface>Entry Box</interface> below the <interface>blackboard</"
"interface>, or click them with the &LMB; and the letters will move down to "
"the entry box. If you are correct, the next anagram appears, otherwise all "
"the letters jump back onto the blackboard."
msgstr ""
"Ko menite, da poznate pravilen odgovor, vnesite črke v <interface>Entry Box</"
"interface> pod <interface>tablo</interface> ali jih kliknite z &LMB; in črke "
"se bodo premaknile navzdol v polje za vnos. Če ste pravilni, se prikaže "
"naslednji anagram, sicer se vse črke vrnejo nazaj na tablo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kanagram;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kanagram;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> dialog is opened by clicking on the "
"<guiicon>Configure</guiicon> button:"
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel> odprete s klikom na gumb "
"<guiicon>Konfiguriraj</guiicon>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kanagram; general settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kanagram; splošne nastavitve</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; general settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram; splošne nastavitve</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Auto-hide hints after:</guilabel> drop down box allows you to "
"specify how hints are presented to you. Here, you can set the hint box to "
"disappear after a certain amount of seconds (&eg; 5 seconds), or you can "
"leave it as default (<quote>Do Not Auto-Hide Hints</quote>)."
msgstr ""
"Spustno polje <guilabel>Samodejno skrij namige po:</guilabel> vam omogoča, "
"da določite, kako vam bodo namigi prikazani. Tukaj lahko nastavite, da polje "
"z namigom izgine po določenem času (&eg; 5 sekund), ali pa ga pustite "
"privzeto (<quote>Ne skrij samodejno namigov</quote>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Time for resolving the anagram:</guilabel> drop down box "
"to specify the time you have to resolve each puzzle. By default there is "
"<quote>No time limit</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite spustno polje <guilabel>Čas za razrešitev anagrama:</guilabel>, da "
"določite čas, ki ga imate za razrešitev posamezne uganke. Privzeto je "
"<quote>Brez časovne omejitve</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Play Using:</guilabel> drop down box allows you to play "
"&kanagram; using vocabularies of a different language. For this feature to "
"work, you must have vocabularies of a separate language installed."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni <guilabel>Predvajaj z:</guilabel> vam omogoča predvajanje "
"&kanagram; uporabo besedišča drugega jezika. Da bi ta funkcija delovala, "
"morate imeti nameščene besednjake ločenega jezika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Set timer for scoring purpose:</guilabel> drop down box allows "
"you to set in seconds the time interval of the scoring timer."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni <guilabel>Nastavi časovnik za namen točkovanja:</guilabel> vam "
"omogoča, da v sekundah nastavite časovni interval časovnika točkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Score Point Settings</guilabel> checkbox can be used to reveal "
"or hide options to configure scoring of answers."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Nastavitve točke</guilabel> lahko uporabite za "
"razkrivanje ali skrivanje možnosti za konfiguracijo točkovanja odgovorov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Use sounds</guilabel> check box allows you to either allow or "
"suppress sound effects."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Uporabi zvoke</guilabel> vam omogoča, da "
"dovolite ali onemogočite zvočne učinke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Only uppercase letters</guilabel> check box allows you to "
"switch &kanagram; to the uppercase only mode for words on the blackboard."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Samo velike črke</guilabel> omogoča preklop "
"&kanagram; na način samo z velikimi črkami za besede na tabli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Say correct words</guilabel> check box allows you to turn "
"pronunciations on or off. The audio files of the pronunciations should be "
"included in the vocabulary being played, or else you should install and "
"configure &jovie; for this option to work."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje <guilabel>Izgovori pravilne besede</guilabel> vam omogoča, "
"da vklopite ali izklopite izgovorjavo. Zvočne datoteke izgovorov je treba "
"vključiti v besedišče, ki se predvaja, sicer morate namestiti in "
"konfigurirati &jovie; da bo ta možnost delovala."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabularies"
msgstr "Besednjaki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Vocabularies</guilabel> configuration page allows you to "
"manage your installed vocabularies. Using this dialog, you can <action>edit</"
"action> and <action>remove</action> downloaded vocabularies, as well as "
"<action>create</action> your very own:"
msgstr ""
"Nastavitvena stran <guilabel>Besednjaki</guilabel> vam omogoča upravljanje "
"nameščenih besednjakov. S tem pogovornim oknom lahko <action>urejate</"
"action> in <action>odstranjujete</action> prenesene besednjake ter "
"<action>ustvarite</action> svojega lastnega:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kanagram; vocabulary settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kanagram; nastavitve besedišča</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; vocabulary settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram; nastavitve besedišča</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Create New</guibutton> button <action>opens the <link linkend="
"\"vocab-editor\"><guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel></link> dialog</"
"action> so that you can author your own vocabularies which you can then play "
"with."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Ustvari novo</guibutton> <action>odpre pogovorno okno <link "
"linkend=\"vocab-editor\"><guilabel>Urejevalnik besednjaka</guilabel></link></"
"action>, da lahko ustvarite svoj lastne besednjake, s katerimi se lahko nato "
"igrate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button allows you to <action>make changes to "
"vocabularies that you have either created or downloaded off the Internet</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> vam omogoča, da <action>spremenite "
"besednjake, ki ste jih ustvarili ali prenesli z interneta</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select which vocabulary you would like to apply these actions to by "
"using the <interface>list of vocabularies</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo <interface>seznama besednjakov</interface> lahko izberete, za "
"kateri besednjak želite uporabiti ta dejanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik besednjaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Vocabulary Editor allows you to create your own vocabularies, which "
"&kanagram; can then test you with:"
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik besednjaka vam omogoča ustvarjanje lastnih besednjakov, ki jih "
"&kanagram; te lahko nato preizkusi z:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kanagram; <guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel></screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kanagram; <guilabel>Urejevalnik besednjaka</guilabel></"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; <guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel></phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kanagram; <guilabel>Urejevalnik besednjaka</guilabel></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Vocabulary Name:</guilabel> field lets you <action>name your "
"vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"Polje <guilabel>Ime besednjaka:</guilabel> vam omogoča <action>poimenovanje "
"vašega besednjaka</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Description:</guilabel> field enables you to <action>expand "
"your vocabulary name</action>, providing the user with more details of the "
"content of your vocabulary."
msgstr ""
"Polje <guilabel>Opis:</guilabel> vam omogoča, da <action>razširite ime "
"svojega besednjaka</action> in tako uporabniku ponudite več podrobnosti o "
"vsebini vašega besednjaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to keep both the name and description fields as short as possible. "
"Effective vocabularies cover a narrow, focused set of words for a single "
"subject. Try to write at least 20 words for your vocabulary, so that it will "
"not be finished too quickly."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite ohraniti čim krajša polja z imenom in opisom. Učinkoviti "
"besednjaki pokrivajo ozek, osredotočen nabor besed za en predmet. Poskusite "
"napisati vsaj 20 besed za svoj besednjak, da ga ne bo prehitro konec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Remove Word</guibutton> button lets you <action>remove words "
"from your vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Odstrani besedo</guibutton> vam omogoča "
"<action>odstranjevanje besed iz vašega besednjaka</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>New Word</guibutton> button <action>creates a new word entry "
"in your vocabulary</action>, ready for you to expand."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Nova beseda</guibutton> <action>ustvari novo besedo v vašem "
"besednjaku</action>, pripravljeno za razširitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Word:</guilabel> field lets you <action>write word values into "
"your vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"Polje <guilabel>Beseda:</guilabel> vam omogoča <action>zapis vrednosti besed "
"v vaš besednjak</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Hint</guilabel> field allows you to <action>write hints to "
"accompany your words</action>."
msgstr ""
"Polje <guilabel>Namig</guilabel> vam omogoča, da <action>napišete namige, ki "
"spremljajo vaše besede</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Good hints clearly yet subtly describe the word, while also increasing the "
"knowledge of the user. Also ensure that your hints are fairly short (under "
"40 characters in length)."
msgstr ""
"Dobri namigi jasno, a subtilno opišejo besedo, hkrati pa povečujejo znanje "
"uporabnika. Poskrbite tudi, da bodo vaši namigi dokaj kratki (manj kot 40 "
"znakov)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button <action>saves your new vocabulary "
"content</action>, and enables its use directly in &kanagram; (it will "
"immediately become available within the application, selectable via. the "
"<interface>Vocabulary Selector</interface>)."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> <action>shranjuje vašo novo vsebino "
"besednjaka</action> in omogoča njeno uporabo neposredno v &kanagram; (takoj "
"bo na voljo v aplikaciji, izbirati ga bo mogoče preko <interface>Izbirnika "
"besednjaka</interface>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button <action>closes the "
"<guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel> dialog</action> without saving the "
"content of your new or modified vocabulary."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton> <action>zapre pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Urejevalnik besednjaka</guilabel></action> brez shranjevanja "
"vsebine vašega novega ali spremenjenega besednjaka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Stuff"
msgstr "Nove stvari"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Download new vocabulary</guibutton> button on the "
"<guilabel>Vocabularies</guilabel> configuration page allows you to obtain "
"new vocabulary files from the Internet:"
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Prenesi nov besednjak</guibutton> na konfiguracijski strani "
"<guilabel>Besednjaki</guilabel> vam omogoča pridobivanje novih datotek "
"besednjaka iz interneta:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kanagram; new stuff dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kanagram; pogovorno okno za nove stvari</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; new stuff dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram; pogovorno okno za nove stvari</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install a vocabulary from the Internet, click on the vocabulary item in "
"the list, then press the <guibutton>Install</guibutton> button to install to "
"your system. The downloaded vocabulary will then be available to play "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"Če želite namestiti besednjak iz interneta, kliknite element besednjaka na "
"seznamu in nato pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Namesti</guibutton> za namestitev "
"v vaš sistem. Preneseni besednjak bo nato takoj na voljo za predvajanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have already downloaded a vocabulary this button will change to "
"<guibutton>Uninstall</guibutton> which allows you to remove a vocabulary."
msgstr ""
"Če ste že prenesli besednjak, se bo ta gumb spremenil v <guibutton>Odstrani</"
"guibutton>, kar vam omogoča odstranitev besednjaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get more information about a vocabulary like the author, a description "
"about the content, and the changelog, press the <guibutton>Details</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o besednjaku, kot je avtor, opis vsebine in dnevnik "
"sprememb, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Podrobnosti</guibutton>."

